### Key Concept
Cloud Storage Lifecycle Management allows you to automatically transition objects between storage classes and delete them based on their age from creation.

### Real-world Example
Lifecycle configuration:
```json
{
  "lifecycle": {
    "rule": [
      {
        "action": {
          "type": "SetStorageClass",
          "storageClass": "COLDLINE"
        },
        "condition": {
          "age": 90
        }
      },
      {
        "action": {
          "type": "Delete"
        },
        "condition": {
          "age": 365
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

### Why This Works
- Age calculated from creation date.
- Actions execute independently.
- Automatic management.
- No manual intervention needed.

